{"tid":619151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地科學院研究多能幹細胞可以返老還童！？","createTime":"2018-04-06T11:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T04:47:48.000Z","uid":40152,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae195463561b99e08ee4fe5e4592e4167d907f6","tid":619151,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"中國科學院的研究團隊在經過5年的鑽研後，日前在國際幹細胞雜誌《細胞‧幹細胞》發表有關成果，透過藥物來調節細胞染色質，將體細胞轉為具自行再生能力的多能幹細胞，類型包括在體外極難培育的肝細胞。研究人員形容，研究結果揭示更簡單、高效、標準化地製備幹細胞的方法。<br />\n<br />\n是次研究由中國科學院廣州生物醫藥與健康研究院研究員裴端卿所帶領。研究人員要先採用一組藥物將體細胞「解鎖」，再以另一組藥物驅動至多能幹細胞的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n裴端卿表示，多能幹細胞具有自我更新、複製能力，並且有再生各種組織器官的潛在功能；而今次研究成果，過程較簡單，所需的初始細胞數量亦較少，且容易標準化，故有助日後廣泛應用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180406/s00004/1523008052812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180406%2Fs00004%2F1523008052812&d=8GNVODSvOC4A%2BY92yGhwoP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=49f9d5fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180406%2Fs00004%2F1523008052812&h=e5b90063\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180406/s00004/1523008052812</a>"},{"pid":"623632bfea748f3bd841465f43b55aa0e17bd9d8","tid":619151,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"唔係信啊"},{"pid":"2c21c7d3ae03c6102d4c11c14a31477dbb73768e","tid":619151,"uid":127447,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"623632bfea748f3bd841465f43b55aa0e17bd9d8","tid":619151,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"唔係信啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"「內地」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass